(6, '/Upload/2016/1013/57ff018b6fec5.png', 6, '网站安全之xss检测与防范', '李黑帅', 0, '今天在朋友的检测下发现了博客留言板的一个xss漏洞,所以把这个记录下来,警示自己也能提醒他人\r\n\r\n技术交流群：456605791', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;今天在朋友的检测下发现了博客留言板的一个xss漏洞,所以把这个记录下来,警示自己也能提醒他人&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;技术交流群：456605791&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;检测方法:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;在表单里面输入如下代码&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:js;toolbar:false&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 9.5px; overflow: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;script&amp;gt;alert(&amp;#39;我是一直快乐的xss漏洞&amp;#39;);&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;结果如下图:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161013/1476329810262493.png&quot; title=&quot;1476329810262493.png&quot; alt=&quot;1458712082632373.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;解决方法:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;在读取的时候加上如下代码即可解决&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:php;toolbar:false&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 9.5px; overflow: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;htmlentities()&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;感谢阅读和陪伴,如果有漏的地方欢迎补刀&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1476329893, 99, 1),
(3, '/Upload/2016/1013/57ff002293a7d.jpg', 6, '挺看的验证码类', '李黑帅', 0, '感觉挺好看的一个验证码类，分享出来大家一起玩玩，后续会加入图片验证，汉字验证等功能', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;感觉挺好看的一个验证码类，分享出来大家一起玩玩，后续会加入图片验证，汉字验证等功能&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;php技术学习交流群：456605791&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:cpp;toolbar:false&quot;&gt;/**\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@author&amp;nbsp;普修米洛斯&amp;nbsp;www.php63.cc\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;int&amp;nbsp;$width&amp;nbsp;宽度\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;int&amp;nbsp;$height&amp;nbsp;高度\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;int&amp;nbsp;$font_size&amp;nbsp;字体大小\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;int&amp;nbsp;$code_len&amp;nbsp;验证码长度\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;int&amp;nbsp;$line_num&amp;nbsp;线条长度\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;string&amp;nbsp;$font&amp;nbsp;字体名称\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;int&amp;nbsp;$interference&amp;nbsp;雪花数量\r\n&amp;nbsp;*/\r\npublic&amp;nbsp;function&amp;nbsp;code($width&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;140,&amp;nbsp;$height&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;60,&amp;nbsp;$font_size&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;16,&amp;nbsp;$code_len&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;5,&amp;nbsp;$line_num&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;8,&amp;nbsp;$font&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;5.ttf&amp;#39;,&amp;nbsp;$interference&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;80){\r\n	$image&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;imagecreatetruecolor($width,&amp;nbsp;$height);\r\n	$image_color&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;imagecolorallocate($image,mt_rand(157,255),&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(157,255),&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(157,255));\r\n	imagefilledrectangle($image,0,$height,$width,0,$image_color);\r\n	$x&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;$width/$code_len;\r\n	for($i&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;0;&amp;nbsp;$i&amp;lt;$code_len;$i++){\r\n		$str&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;ABCDEFGHJKLMNPQRSTUVWXYZ23456789&amp;#39;;\r\n		$font_color&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;imagecolorallocate($image,mt_rand(0,156),mt_rand(0,156),mt_rand(0,156));\r\n		$url&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;LIB_PATH.&amp;#39;Lib/Code/&amp;#39;.$font,utf8_encode($str[mt_rand(0,strlen($str)-1)]);\r\n		imagettftext($image,$font_size,mt_rand(-30,30),$x*$i+mt_rand(1,3),$height&amp;nbsp;/&amp;nbsp;1.4,$font_color,$url);\r\n	}\r\n	//生成线条\r\n	for($i&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;0;$i&amp;lt;$line_num;$i++)&amp;nbsp;{\r\n		$line_color&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;imagecolorallocate($image,&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(0,&amp;nbsp;156),&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(0,&amp;nbsp;156),&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(0,&amp;nbsp;156));\r\n		imageline($image,&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(0,$width),mt_rand(0,$height),mt_rand(0,$width),mt_rand(0,$height),&amp;nbsp;$line_color);\r\n	}\r\n	for($i=0;$i&amp;lt;$interference;$i++){\r\n		$color&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;imagecolorallocate($image,&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(200,&amp;nbsp;255),&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(200,&amp;nbsp;255),&amp;nbsp;mt_rand(200,&amp;nbsp;255));\r\n		imagestring($image,mt_rand(1,5),mt_rand(0,$width),mt_rand(0,$height),&amp;#39;*&amp;#39;,$color);\r\n	}\r\n	header(&amp;quot;Content-type:&amp;nbsp;image/png&amp;quot;);\r\n	imagepng($image);\r\n	imagedestroy($image);\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1476324740, 99, 1),
(4, '/Upload/2016/1013/57ff0004718b1.jpg', 6, '权限管理系统配置教程', '李黑帅', 0, '因为好多人拿到权限管理系统不会使用,所以出了个简单的教程,其实和正常的Tp一样', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;工具：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;1.wampserver&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 2.权限管理系统&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;一.服务器基础配置&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; 1.编辑C:\\Windows\\System32\\Drivers\\etc下的hosts文件并添加自己希望设置的域名如图1:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161013/1476327713280222.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1476327713280222.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;QQ截图20161013110136.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;注：为了不影响正常上网，通常我们用io作为后缀&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; 2.然后打开D:\\wamp\\bin\\apache\\apache2.4.9\\conf下的httpd.conf搜索#Include conf/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf然后去掉#号，这样就相当于引入httpd-vhosts.conf然后保存关闭，如图二&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161013/1476327852104829.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1476327852104829.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;QQ截图20161013110401.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;3.编辑D:\\wamp\\bin\\apache\\apache2.4.9\\conf\\extra\\httpd-vhosts.conf如下图&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161013/1476327903336508.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1476327903336508.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;QQ截图20161013110454.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:php;toolbar:false&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;VirtualHost&amp;nbsp;*:80&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;DocumentRoot&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;D:/Leo/www/blog&amp;quot;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;ServerName&amp;nbsp;blog.io\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;ServerAlias&amp;nbsp;blog.io\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;Directory&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;D:/Leo/www/blog&amp;quot;&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Options&amp;nbsp;FollowSymLinks\r\n			AllowOverride&amp;nbsp;all\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;		Require&amp;nbsp;all&amp;nbsp;granted\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/Directory&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;/VirtualHost&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; 4.重启服务器即可&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;二.站点配置&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 1.将权限系统放入站点根目录如下图:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src=&quot;/ueditor/php/upload/image/20161013/1476328326796561.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1476328326796561.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;QQ截图20161013111027.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;2.把下面的内容保存为.htaccess文件放到应用入口文件的同级目录下&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:php;toolbar:false&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;IfModule&amp;nbsp;mod_rewrite.c&amp;gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;RewriteEngine&amp;nbsp;on\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;RewriteCond&amp;nbsp;%{REQUEST_FILENAME}&amp;nbsp;!-d\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;RewriteCond&amp;nbsp;%{REQUEST_FILENAME}&amp;nbsp;!-f\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;RewriteRule&amp;nbsp;^(.*)$&amp;nbsp;index.php/$1&amp;nbsp;[QSA,PT,L]\r\n&amp;lt;/IfModule&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;3.导入数据库&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 默认数据库名称为auth 密码为qwertyuiop不建议更改表前缀&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 导入成功后,配置数据库连接文件即可正常登陆&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;注意： 不要直接在数据表内更改密码，默认账号密码为admin admin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1476327634, 99, 1),
(5, '/Upload/2016/1013/57feffe50531b.jpg', 6, 'php下sql server服务器配置', '李黑帅', 0, 'php下配置sql server服务器', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;所用到的工具包：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;1、SQL Server 2008&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;2、phpStudy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3、msodbcsql（odbc驱动）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;4、php_pdo_sqlsrv_55_nts.dll&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;5、php_sqlsrv_55_nts.dll&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;技术交流群：456605791&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;安装步骤&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;1、安装sql环境我这里使用的是sql server 2008&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:html;toolbar:false&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 9.5px; overflow: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;下载地址：http://download.microsoft.com/download/2/0/0/200f927b-45f8-4c44-9391-1f7794503dd6/SQLServer2008_BOL_CHS.msi&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;2、安装时选择sql用户设置相应密码&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;3、搭建php环境，此处我选用phpStudy安装php环境的php5.5版本&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;4、安装对于php扩展，将php_pdo_sqlsrv_55_nts.dll和php_sqlsrv_55_nts.dll复制到phpStudy\\php55n\\ext&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;5、修改配置文件打开phpStudy\\php55n\\php.ini添加extension=php_pdo_sqlsrv_55_nts.dll;extension=php_sqlsrv_55_nts.dll然后重启环境&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;6、运行测试文件代码如下：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:php;toolbar:false&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 9.5px; overflow: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;?php\r\n$serverName=&amp;quot;你服务器地址默认为localhost,1433&amp;quot;;&amp;nbsp;//数据库地址和端口\r\n$database=&amp;quot;testuser&amp;quot;;&amp;nbsp;//数据库名称\r\n$uid=&amp;quot;sa&amp;quot;;&amp;nbsp;//用户名\r\n$pwd=&amp;quot;sasa&amp;quot;;&amp;nbsp;//密码\r\ntry&amp;nbsp;{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$conn&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;new&amp;nbsp;PDO(&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;sqlsrv:server=$serverName;Database&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;$database&amp;quot;,&amp;nbsp;$uid,&amp;nbsp;$pwd);\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$conn-&amp;gt;setAttribute(&amp;nbsp;PDO::ATTR_ERRMODE,&amp;nbsp;PDO::ERRMODE_EXCEPTION&amp;nbsp;);\r\n}catch(&amp;nbsp;PDOException&amp;nbsp;$e&amp;nbsp;)&amp;nbsp;{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;die(&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;Error&amp;nbsp;connecting&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;SQL&amp;nbsp;Server&amp;quot;.$e&amp;nbsp;);\r\n}&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;如果什么也没提示则代表开启成功！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;感谢大家的阅读与陪伴，如有遗漏麻烦提出来下，再见&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1476329122, 99, 1),
(7, '/Upload/2016/1013/57ff0f1cc970e.jpg', 6, '常用正则', '李黑帅', 0, '表单提交为了防止注入通常都要进行过滤,而前端过滤都只是提升用户体验,关键还得靠后台,以下是我常用的正则:技术交流:456605791\r\n\r\n', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;技术交流:&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;456605791&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;表单提交为了防止注入通常都要进行过滤,而前端过滤都只是提升用户体验,关键还得靠后台,以下是我常用的正则:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;brush:php;toolbar:false&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 9.5px; overflow: auto; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;?php\r\n\r\n/**\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;验证字符串是否为6-16位数字字母下划线组成的\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;string&amp;nbsp;$str&amp;nbsp;要验证的字符串\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;string&amp;nbsp;$msg&amp;nbsp;提示消息\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@return&amp;nbsp;bool&amp;nbsp;成功返回true&amp;nbsp;失败直接提示错误信息\r\n&amp;nbsp;*/\r\nfunction&amp;nbsp;is_char_num($str=&amp;#39;&amp;#39;,$msg=&amp;#39;&amp;#39;)\r\n{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if($str&amp;nbsp;==&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;){\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;return&amp;nbsp;true;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;}\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$res&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;preg_match(&amp;#39;/^[_0-9a-z]{6,16}$/i&amp;#39;,$str);\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if(!$res){\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$msg&amp;nbsp;==&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;?&amp;nbsp;$msg&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;请传入提示信息&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;:&amp;nbsp;$msg;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;error($msg);\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;}\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;return&amp;nbsp;true;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;$tel&amp;nbsp;验证手机号或者电话号\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@return&amp;nbsp;bool&amp;nbsp;成功返回true\r\n&amp;nbsp;*/\r\nfunction&amp;nbsp;is_tel($tel)\r\n{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$isMob=&amp;quot;/^1[3-5,7,8]{1}[0-9]{9}$/&amp;quot;;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$isTel=&amp;quot;/^([0-9]{3,4}-)?[0-9]{7,8}$/&amp;quot;;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if(!preg_match($isMob,$tel)&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;!preg_match($isTel,$tel))\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;error(&amp;quot;手机或电话号码格式不正确。如果是固定电话，必须形如(xxxx-xxxxxxxx)!&amp;quot;);\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;}\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;return&amp;nbsp;true;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@param&amp;nbsp;$email&amp;nbsp;验证邮件\r\n&amp;nbsp;*&amp;nbsp;@return&amp;nbsp;bool&amp;nbsp;成功返回true\r\n&amp;nbsp;*/\r\nfunction&amp;nbsp;is_email($email)\r\n{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;$pattern&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;/^([0-9A-Za-z\\\\-_\\\\.]+)@([0-9a-z]+\\\\.[a-z]{2,3}(\\\\.[a-z]{2})?)$/i&amp;quot;;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if&amp;nbsp;(!preg_match(&amp;nbsp;$pattern,&amp;nbsp;$email&amp;nbsp;)&amp;nbsp;)&amp;nbsp;{\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;error(&amp;#39;请输入正确的邮箱地址&amp;#39;);\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;}\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;return&amp;nbsp;true;\r\n}\r\n?&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;感谢大家的阅读与陪伴，如有遗漏麻烦提出来下，再见&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1476333345, 99, 1);
INSERT INTO `a_article` (`id`, `img`, `cid`, `title`, `author`, `type`, `desc`, `content`, `addtime`, `sort`, `status`) VALUES
(8, '/Upload/2016/1013/57ff0ff22146f.jpg', 3, '基于ThinkPHP3.2.3的一款权限管理系统', '李黑帅', 0, '基于ThinkPHP3.2.3的一款权限管理系统', '&lt;h3 style=&quot;white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;项目说明&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;本系统是一个基于Thinkphp3.2.3框架开发的一个轻量级后台管理系统，是为了简化项目和快速开发为目的而开发的，很多项目都会用到本系统，这套系统能大量减少重复开发量，提高团队开发效率，减少公司开发成本，同时公开本项目是本着学习为目的和同行多多交流，如果需要数据库请加QQ群：456605791。&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;超级管理账号:admin&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;超级管理密码:admin&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;&quot;&gt;欢迎大家加入:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;&quot;&gt;456605791&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;&quot;&gt;源码下载&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;https://github.com/liuzhongsheng/auth&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 32px;&quot;&gt;数据库请进入Q群联系管理员获取&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;anchor&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/liuzhongsheng/auth#优势&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 120, 192); text-decoration: none; float: left; padding-right: 4px; margin-left: -20px; line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;优势&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;1.大量节省开发时间&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;2.缩短开发周期&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3.减少重复开发量&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &amp;quot;Apple Color Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Emoji&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI Symbol&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;4.提高团队开发效率&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1